post 1: Tonight I discovered that if you hang out with a bunch of people who you were friends with in school but haven't seen for approximately.... 30 mumble years...., you will spend a LOT of the time feeling just as awkward as you did when you were a teenager, a LOT of the time comparing your current need for reading glasses and/or perimenopausal symptoms, and a LOT of the time feeling as though you've blocked out half your memories.
post 2: 40 today! Happy birthday to S. At what point do you think people will stop saying "but you look about 12"? ?? Have a great day and I'll see you later for the birthday surprise.
